data.description: Prepare to be wowed by this outstanding and meticulously kept property on half an acre, IN TOWN! This home boasts not only a fantastic location but also an abundance of space and personality. Step inside and discover a main floor designed for both productivity and relaxation. The separate entry office space is ideal for those who work from home, providing the perfect environment for focus and creativity. And when it's time to unwind, the expansive living room awaits, seamlessly connected to a screened-in patio where you can soak up the sunshine and fresh air. Entertaining is a breeze in this home, thanks to its spacious layout and convenient amenities. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or a casual gathering, you'll love the flow of this space and the ease with which you can move from indoors to outdoors. And let's talk about location – situated on a generous double-corner lot, you'll enjoy easy access to all the shopping and dining options that downtown Morton has to offer. Plus, with so many updates throughout the home, including a main floor primary bedroom with main floor laundry, stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, and a two-car garage with an attached workshop, you'll have everything you need for modern comfort and convenience. Don't miss out on this incredible value and make this eclectic and personality-filled home yours before it's gone!
